            <div class="sf"><strong>IAM & MFA</strong><span>Azure AD, Okta, authentification forte, SSO</span></div>
            <div class="sf"><strong>ZTNA</strong><span>Remplacement du VPN, accès contextuel aux ressources</span></div>
            <div class="sf"><strong>Microsegmentation</strong><span>Isolation des workloads, East-West traffic control</span></div>
            <div class="sf"><strong>PAM</strong><span>Gestion des accès privilégiés, coffre-fort de mots de passe</span></div>
