          <div class="zt-pill"><div class="zt-pill-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>Inspection & log de chaque flux, IA d'anomalies</div>
          <div class="zt-pill"><div class="zt-pill-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg></div>Microsegmentation — isolation des workloads critiques</div>
