    <div class="sectors-grid reveal">
      <div class="sec-card"><div class="sec-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2"/><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="16"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="14" y2="14"/></svg></div><h3>Banque & Finance</h3><p>Conformité DORA, SWIFT CSP, segmentation stricte, supervision des flux sensibles.</p></div>
